  "original_title": "HUTCH offers FREE Talk Time relief to its subscribers",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "HUTCH offers FREE Talk Time relief to its subscribers",
      "author": "Thilina Walpola",
      "body_lines": [
        "HUTCH, the country\u2019s rapidly-growing choice for communication services has understood the great difficulties being faced by its customers during the present economic crisis with rapidly increasing costs. To provide some relief to its valued subscribers. Hutch has introduced the \u2018HUTCH Relief Recharge Bonus\u2019 program offering subscribers customers up to 100% bonus Talk Time on their recharges.",
        "The program is part of a number of other initiatives Hutch has been rolling out to support subscribers during these economically strained times.",
        "Thirukumar Nadarasa, CEO of HUTCH commenting on the offering stated, \u201cUnder the prevailing economic circumstances, people are facing difficulties both financially and in their mobility to access recharges for their phone. We have therefore rolled out this program to provide our customers more talk time value for their money, and in turn also reduce the need to frequently visit recharge outlets to top up their account\u201d.",
        "Hutch Prepaid customers will receive FREE Talk Time Bonuses up to 100% on specific denominated recharge values ranging from Rs 250 to Rs 1050 offering up to 500 mins of Any-network Free Talk time valid up to 30 days.",
        "SLT Training Centre offers world-class BEng (Hons) Degree by University of Hertfordshire UK",
        "Bank of Ceylon celebrates 83rd Anniversary steering strongly and steadily",
        "Leave a Reply Cancel replyYour email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *Comment Name *",
        "Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment."
